{"TopicId":176946,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Delay Fuses","CreatedByName":"Cheif Operations Director","CreatedById":183218,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-07-23T02:54:33Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Cheif Operations Director","CreatedById":183218,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-07-23T02:54:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHaving a delay fuse on engines and staging would be so useful. When I seperate a booster having the ability to deplay a parachute without actually being there or when using seperatons to successfully seperate funny boosters would be very useful.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DoctorDavinci","CreatedById":150019,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-07-23T03:27:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed3555780131\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/151340-14x-smart-parts-continued/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:226px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"4x4cheesecake","CreatedById":187982,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-07-23T04:29:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI would love to see a delay function for parts. A slider in the part action menu to set a timer like it is done in the \u0027Kaboom\u0027 mod and we could put a whole launch sequenz into a single action group \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E Fire the main engines, release the launch clamps and cut external fuel lines 10 sec. later, wait for additional 2 secs and fire the booster...with just a single button \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:o\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon2.png\u0022 title=\u00